Introduction to Data Science\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]]\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.807444766360592*^9, 3.807444783971064*^9}, {
  3.807444845902679*^9, 
  3.807444847393783*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b1b89504-4eee-4113-90f2-\
8f66e706d782"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
In the real world data can be \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]dirty\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] (incomplete, noisy, inconsistent) and needs to be \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]cleaned\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777363308339382*^9, 3.777363377167943*^9}, {
  3.8085449141295557`*^9, 3.808544947761919*^9}, {3.808545060623262*^9, 
  3.808545076693195*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f3622847-4c8a-447e-814b-\
e80ed2ab515a"],

Cell["Incomplete: attribute values lacking", "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777363308339382*^9, 3.777363377167943*^9}, {
  3.8085449141295557`*^9, 
  3.808544967808558*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"4584e1d7-5c71-4962-b9f6-\
8a03fcc5ce56"],

Cell["\<\
Noisy: outliers due to random fluctuations or real extreme events due to \
natural sources\
\>", "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777363308339382*^9, 3.777363377167943*^9}, {
  3.8085449141295557`*^9, 
  3.80854503416764*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"a8352e72-1953-4867-a1eb-\
f8b3b57e0132"],

Cell["\<\
Inconsistent: data contains discrepancies in codes or names. For example, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]name\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] column does not contains \
alphabetical letters.     \.00\
\>", "Subitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777363308339382*^9, 3.777363377167943*^9}, {
  3.8085449141295557`*^9, 3.80854504416094*^9}, {3.808548081852321*^9, 
  3.8085481369291*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"0d340ef9-508c-4612-b91c-f86b95e6a47a"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Garbage in, Garbage out principle: messy data will yield messy analytical \
models. \
\>", "Item",
